'''Edvin Biuković''' ([[June 22]], [[1960s#1969|1969]] &ndash; [[December 5]], [[1999]]) was the penciller of [[Dark Horse Comics]]' [[Star Wars: X-Wing Rogue Squadron: The Phantom Affair (TPB)|''Star Wars: X-Wing Rogue Squadron: The Phantom Affair'']] and the [[The Last Command (TPB)|''Star Wars: The Last Command'']] comic adaptation.

He died in 1999 from complications relating to a brain tumor, which had been diagnosed a few weeks prior to his death.
